g.text: Makes Http Request to get Allergy data
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDV
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Displays the fetched data and asks for the new Allergy's data
Sends Allergy's data (AllergyCode, AllergyName, AllergyDescription, AllergySymptoms)
